original: You're a hot flight attendant, I was drunk
translated: 你是性感的空姐，我当时喝醉了

original: I was the loaded guy in the suit on flight 207 from Los Santos to Liberty City.  I kept asking you to get things out of the overhead locker.  I threw peanuts at the disabled kid.  You told me you would call the police if I didn't stop singing.  I puked in the in-flight magazine and then passed out.  You were wearing lots of make-up and a tight skirt.
translated: 我是从洛圣都飞往自由城的207次航班上的那个西装男。当时喝醉了，一直让你从行李架上拿东西，还朝那个残疾孩子扔花生。你说我再唱下去就要报警了。我吐在了机上杂志里，昏过去了。你化了很厚的妆，穿着紧身裙。
